panels.description: The unit and denomination for the asset bonded in the system
panels.title: Bond denom

panels.description: The time duration required for bonded ATOMs to unbond and become transferrable
panels.title: Unbonding Time, day(s)

panels.description: The maximum number of unbondings between a delegator and validator within the unbonding period
panels.title: Max Entries

panels.description: Historical Entries is the number of historical entries to persist
panels.title: Historical Entries

panels.description: The maximum number of validators that may participate in validating blocks, earning rewards, and governance voting
panels.title: Max Validators

panels.description: The suspension time (aka jail time) for a validator that is offline too long
panels.title: Downtime Jail Duration

panels.description: Minimum proportion of blocks signed per window without being slashed
panels.title: Min Signed Per Window

panels.description: Window for being offline without being slashed, in blocks
panels.title: Signed Block Window

panels.description: Slashing fraction due to double signing
panels.title: Slash Fraction Double Sign

panels.description: Slashing fraction due to downtime
panels.title: Slash Fraction Downtime

panels.description: Denomination of minted tokens
panels.title: Mint Denom

panels.description: Expected number of blocks per year
panels.title: Blocks Per Year

panels.description: The target ratio of bonded stake to total supply
panels.title: Goal Bonded

panels.description: The maximum rate that the Cosmos Hub can mint new ATOMs, proportional to the supply
panels.title: Inflation Max

panels.description: The minimum rate that the Cosmos Hub can mint new ATOMs, proportional to the supply
panels.title: Inflation Min

panels.description: A factor of and limit to the speed at which the Cosmos Hub's inflation rate changes
panels.title: Inflation Rate Change

panels.description: The fixed base reward bonus for the validator proposing a block, as a proportion of transaction fees
panels.title: Base Proposer Reward

panels.description: The maximum additional reward bonus for the validator proposing a block, as a proportion of transaction fees
panels.title: Bonus Proposer Reward

panels.description: The proportion of staking rewards diverted to the community pool
panels.title: Community Tax

panels.description: Determines whether or not delegators may set a separate address for receiving staking rewards
panels.title: Withdraw Address Enabled

panels.description: The minimum deposit required for a proposal to enter the voting period
panels.title: Min Deposit

panels.description: The maximum amount of time that a proposal can accept deposit contributions before expiring
panels.title: Max Deposit Period

panels.description: The minimum proportion of network voting power required for a governance proposal's outcome to be considered valid
panels.title: Quorum

panels.description: The minimum proportion of participating voting power required for a governance proposal to pass
panels.title: Threshold

panels.description: The minimum proportion of participating voting power to veto (ie. fail) a governance proposal
panels.title: Veto Threshold

panels.description: The maximum amount of time that a proposal can accept votes before the voting period concludes
panels.title: Voting Period
